Short Description:
Our mission is provide healthy calories, strengthen community and improve the urban environment through a nationwide network of sustainable little orchards to dramatically increase access to healthy food.

Our Vision:
1) thousands of little orchards in food insecure urban neighborhoods across the nation; 
2) a system of local food production that feeds people for decades; 
3) a national network of neighborhood stewards trained in holistic methods for growing fruit; and
4) urban neighborhoods transformed by their own work and generosity.
